interpretation: The "alien monster" card depicts an extraterrestrial being that is both mysterious and otherworldly. This card represents the unknown and the unfamiliar, encouraging you to embrace the unknown and explore new possibilities. It may also signify feeling like an outsider or being in a situation where you feel like you don't quite fit in. This card reminds you to embrace your uniqueness and embrace your differences. Be open to new experiences and be willing to take risks.
